{"tid":2352502,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"你地第一次認識陳雲，有冇真係覺得佢係隱世高人","createTime":"2021-01-04T05:27:01.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-04T06:34:12.000Z","uid":54930,"like":5,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"7ec02e002d5d0c165243fd9c9529003f7bdbbe51","tid":2352502,"uid":54930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-04T05:27:01.000Z","msg":"第一次係連登睇到人轉貼佢既post<br />\n講野有文有路，引經據典，滿腹經論<br />\n真係覺得佢係再世諸葛亮，香港國師<br />\n雖然佢fb 個profile pic人甩皮甩骨，<br />\n但係諸葛亮當年何嘗唔係一介村夫<br />\n到佢宣佈出山參選，我直頭覺得熱狗就係三顧茅廬，準備打天下，香港有救<br />\n<br />\n當知一個唔覺意輸左，仲痴埋，從此變左未食藥顛佬<br />\n<br />\nbtw，係度多謝陳雲未顛之前呢幾年既付出，為左救香港蒼生而放棄高薪教席<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/noodles.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n附上陳雲profile pic<br />\n<img src=\"https://encrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn:ANd9GcQbL8djpawrxu5lqafN6IWn2NGl8ctP9GH4vw&amp;usqp=CAU\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fencrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com%2Fimages%3Fq%3Dtbn%3AANd9GcQbL8djpawrxu5lqafN6IWn2NGl8ctP9GH4vw%26usqp%3DCAU&h=34dfbeed&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20181216/c6800a72b0f1421a9dc9aad6626e2560.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com%2Fimages%2F20181216%2Fc6800a72b0f1421a9dc9aad6626e2560.jpeg&h=34bb942d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6f29505a620042e6499c662e1b90f95fe3a90bad","tid":2352502,"uid":131157,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-04T05:30:26.000Z","msg":"係連登講算吧啦<br />\n到今時今日仲係度講咩封關，咁要封關閘係個病好嚴重啦？ 咁政府咪順水推舟同你玩大佢，遲d 要強制你安裝安心出行，冇健康碼唔洗諗住出境<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"834e135c8dc88e28bf6274abe16980d552bc5f12","tid":2352502,"uid":225542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score"